Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:07.26,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Over a hundred years ago, ☮[Phr0stYsuBs]☮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:10.73,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,humanity suddenly found itself\Nfaced with a new predator.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:20.88,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,They were far more powerful than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.67,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Humanity was immediately pushed\Nto the brink of extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The survivors built three walls:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, Rose, and Sina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There, they enjoyed a century of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That Day\NThe Fall of Zhiganshina (2)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:35.55,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,"For till then I was a\Nsoul in misery, alienate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:40.51,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,From God, and covetous\Nof all earthly things;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:43.60,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,Now, as thou seest,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.13,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,here punish'd for my doting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:54.56,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,Such cleansing from the taint of avarice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:56.70,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,Do spirits, converted, need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:02.31,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,This mount inflicts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.77,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,No direr penalty."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.28,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.51,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.43,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,"O avarice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:27.39,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,What canst thou more,\Nwho hast subdued our blood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:33.10,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,So wholly to thyself, they feel no care
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.41,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,Of their own flesh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.17,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,O avarice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:44.10,Default,ThisFucker,0,0,0,,What canst thou more, who hastÃ¢Â€Â”"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.95,Default,H,0,0,0,,Eren, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.89,Default,E,0,0,0,,We were so close\Nto saving my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.15,Default,E,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:06.91,Default,E,0,0,0,,We almost saved my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.51,Default,H,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:10.85,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.32,Default,H,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:23.09,Default,H,0,0,0,,The reason you couldn't save your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you lacked the strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.79,Default,H,0,0,0,,The reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:34.63,Default,H,0,0,0,,The reason I didn't fight the Titan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:38.09,Default,H,0,0,0,,was that I lacked the courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.47,Default,H,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,Ah, it's happening again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.13,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.46,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,To the inner gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:26.20,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Use all ships at the pier\Nfor Zhiganshina's evacuation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.95,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hurry! They'll eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:45.31,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,There are small areas that protrude,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,like Zhiganshina, all around the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.62,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Their purpose is to attract the Titans,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,thus reducing the cost and\Nmanpower of defending the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.98,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,After the people of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:06:01.10,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Zhiganshina had fulfilled their function,\Nby drawing the Titans to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:04.48,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,they were forced to\Nevacuate by a single gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.28,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't bring anything aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.89,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We're taking as many people as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.50,Default,Hat,0,0,0,,Armin, sit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:20.59,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.39,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren and Mikasa aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.98,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.50,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.70,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't talk to them just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Poor kids...\NGoing by appearances, it must've been bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.12,Default,H,0,0,0,,Why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.50,Default,H,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.34,Default,H,0,0,0,,Where are those cannon shells?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.32,Default,H,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.23,Default,H,0,0,0,,They're right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:13.49,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,This just can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.54,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Oh God, oh God, oh God...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.61,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.85,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The ship's full!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.01,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,It's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:24.88,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.17,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Please, at least take my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.21,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.48,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.41,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Let him on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:36.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Let us on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:53.85,Default,H,0,0,0,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:55.18,Default,H,0,0,0,,Where are you aiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:59.24,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,B-But this thing doesn't\Nhave that kind of accuracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:02.17,Default,H,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't give a crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.99,Default,H,0,0,0,,Just load the next shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.69,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:12.91,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,It's closing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.21,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,We need to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.51,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,We'll be left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:16.22,Default,H,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.19,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't close it yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.72,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wait a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:23.57,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Many people are still in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.58,Default,OtherGuy,0,0,0,,If they break through this gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll lose more than a\Nsingle city to the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:33.08,Default,OtherGuy,0,0,0,,We'll lose the entire\Nterritory within this wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:36.70,Default,H,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean we\Ncan let these people die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.10,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Close the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.24,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,The Titans are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.06,Default,OtherGuy,0,0,0,,Get that gate shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.46,Default,H,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.74,Default,H,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:33.55,Default,H,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.64,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.80,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.40,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,It's coming! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:56.20,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The Titan's coming!\NIt's going to ram the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.66,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Close the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.16,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:57.97,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Information We Can Share So Far:\N\NRough Diagram of Human Territory (1)\NDiagram (see original work) broadly depicts\Narea still inhabited by humans.\NArea outside Wall Maria remains a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:02.97,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Information We Can Share So Far:\N\NRough Diagram of Human Territory (2)\NElevation increases with relative proximity\Nto the center of human territory.\NTerritory is rich in natural resources,\Nsuch as water, minerals, and natural gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:08.69,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Several hours after Zhiganshina's\Nfall on Wall Maria's south side,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:12.98,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,the news had spread throughout
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.00,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,the entire human territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:16.88,Default,Suit,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:20.57,Default,Suit,0,0,0,,Wall Rose, South Side\NTrost District
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.14,Default,Suit,0,0,0,,Have Titans entered Zhiganshina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.45,Default,Suit,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.16,Default,Suit,0,0,0,,Why would walls that have\Nlasted a century fall now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.66,Default,Offscreendude,0,0,0,,Whether you believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,there are people out there\Nwho escaped by ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.88,Default,Offscreendude,0,0,0,,At least five hundred, I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:37.30,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,The question is if we've\Nlost Zhiganshina alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:42.97,Default,Mustache,0,0,0,,But they would certainly never\Npenetrate Wall Maria, would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:46.93,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,At the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.85,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,we should contact the central\Ngovernment and await orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.23,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,We cannot handle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.63,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,an emergency such as this on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.27,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.32,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,A messenger just arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:02.73,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,They say Wall Maria has been breached!\NThe Titans are invading!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:12.23,Default,H,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.21,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:19.63,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Humanity will be devoured by Titans again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.48,Default,E,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:28.56,Default,E,0,0,0,,I can never go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.19,Default,E,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.93,Default,E,0,0,0,,Why did I waste my final minutes with\Nher having some stupid argument?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:40.78,Default,E,0,0,0,,Now she's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.11,Default,E,0,0,0,,She's never coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:48.13,Default,E,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:52.29,Default,H,0,0,0,,You lacked the strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.72,Default,M,0,0,0,,Because humans are weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.86,Default,M,0,0,0,,Is crying all that we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.55,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'll kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.15,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:21.96,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.11,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.36,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:33.15,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'll wipe every one of them...\Noff the face of this earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:50.24,Default,E,0,0,0,,That year, the central government decided\Nto fall back within Wall Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:55.62,Default,E,0,0,0,,During that period of time,\Nthe Titans consumed ten thousand people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:00.26,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Eren... Karla...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.40,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.36,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:09.56,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:11.41,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:12.80,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.28,Default,E,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:16.15,Default,E,0,0,0,,Stop it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.54,Default,E,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:20.90,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Just give me your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.22,Default,E,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:25.21,Default,E,0,0,0,,After Mom died, you lost it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.42,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.55,Default,E,0,0,0,,Let me go, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.03,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,This is for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.64,Default,E,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.35,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Don't forget the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.77,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You must get there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.19,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Someday, you'll understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.48,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Until you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.78,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.27,Default,M,0,0,0,,You were tossing and turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.58,Default,E,0,0,0,,I feel like I saw my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:00.00,Default,M,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.15,Default,M,0,0,0,,It was only a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.34,Default,E,0,0,0,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:08.76,Default,M,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.80,Default,M,0,0,0,,They said they're going to distribute food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:20.23,Default,M,0,0,0,,This was once a food storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:23.48,Default,M,0,0,0,,They're keeping refugees\Nwho fled by ship here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.68,Default,Baldy,0,0,0,,Hey, don't cut in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.54,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.41,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten anything since last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:43.63,Default,M,0,0,0,,It isn't yet certain that we'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.80,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:46.55,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.51,Default,E,0,0,0,,Armin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.04,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.40,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I got here in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:56.23,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,My grandpa got these for us kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.30,Default,M,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.63,Default,E,0,0,0,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.19,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.31,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I don't think there's\Nenough food for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.91,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,They say that's all we'll get today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:15.40,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,There are too many refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.47,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,And not enough food to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:21.11,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,You know the farther out you live,\Nthe less they care, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:25.21,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Why do we have to share\Nour food with outsiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.32,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,If the Titans were breaking through anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,they should have eaten more,\Nso there'd be fewer mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.01,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:40.72,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Now there's just that much less food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:42.34,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.73,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,What are you doing, stupid kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.15,Default,E,0,0,0,,You have no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:53.01,Default,E,0,0,0,,You've never even seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:57.32,Default,E,0,0,0,,You've never seen the\Nway they eat people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:16:59.99,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.12,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:03.91,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,He's just upset because he's hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:07.29,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,That's why he's being so rude to an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:10.38,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I'm r-really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.15,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:19.51,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The only reason you aren't starving\Nis because of us, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.84,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Even a kid should show gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:24.95,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.69,Default,E,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:29.65,Default,E,0,0,0,,No guy like that's looking after me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.40,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'm going back to Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.28,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill all the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:40.87,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren, you aren't serious, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.99,Default,M,0,0,0,,I am serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:46.49,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'm not like them, sitting inside\Nthe walls and acting tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.48,Default,M,0,0,0,,I don't need this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.46,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren, you'll starve!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.99,Default,E,0,0,0,,This doesn't bother you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:59.10,Default,E,0,0,0,,We can't win until we can stop\Ndepending on stuff from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:00.16,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.39,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,We can't beat the Titans, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.24,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do\Nbut live within the walls...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:07.56,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,If you do something dumb, you'll die.\NLike my mom and dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.83,Default,E,0,0,0,,So we should suck up to them instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:11.07,Default,E,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.57,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Right now... Right now, there's no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:15.24,Default,E,0,0,0,,That's just an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:20.16,Default,E,0,0,0,,Then spend the rest of your\Nlife as cattle, weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.50,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Mikasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:38.06,Default,M,0,0,0,,If Armin is a weakling, so are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:44.59,Default,M,0,0,0,,We didn't even run from the Titans\Nor from the city on our own two feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:48.56,Default,M,0,0,0,,We couldn't even get the food\Nwe're eating today without help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:54.36,Default,M,0,0,0,,Anyone so weak couldn't\Npossibly defeat a single Titan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:58.63,Default,M,0,0,0,,What matters is survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:00.87,Default,M,0,0,0,,Just like your mother said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.33,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Mikasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.69,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eat... And survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,I will not let you starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.06,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Several days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:30.58,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,refugees were sent in droves\Nto till the wastelands,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.78,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,to bring in more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:38.07,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,But even still, there wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.53,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,And the following year, in 846,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the central government used many refugees
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in an operation ostensibly\Nto recover Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.55,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Two hundred fifty thousand, in all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.89,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Approximately twenty\Npercent of the population.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:05.26,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,But there were only just\Nover a hundred survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:13.10,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Their sacrifice alleviated the food\Nshortage for the rest of us somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.54,Default,E,0,0,0,,It's all because of the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.50,Default,E,0,0,0,,If we destroy them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we can retake our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:38.90,Default,E,0,0,0,,Armin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.19,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'm enlisting next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:47.93,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'll gain the power to fight Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.02,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.19,Default,E,0,0,0,,Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:55.65,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.44,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'll go, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:01.20,Default,E,0,0,0,,Mikasa, you don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:04.12,Default,E,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that it's\Nimportant to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:07.99,Default,M,0,0,0,,So I'll go, to keep you from dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.22,Default,E,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.21,Default,E,0,0,0,,The three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:27.93,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,We now begin the enlistment ceremony\Nfor the 104th Trainee Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:31.80,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,I am Keith Shadis, and I had the\Nmisfortune to be assigned
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to train you bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.43,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,And I'm not here to welcome you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:41.01,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,Right now, you're mere cattle,\Nfit for nothing but Titan food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:42.94,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,No, less than cattle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:48.49,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,In three years, we'll take you worthless\Npieces of crap and train you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:51.45,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,Give you the means to fight the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:55.55,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,In three years, when you\Nstand before a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.54,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,will you still be food?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:22:01.28,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,Or will you be a noble\Nwall, shielding the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:05.55,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,Or perhaps, one of humanity's\Nglorious soldiers that slay Titans?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.22,Default,Beard,0,0,0,,You will decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:09.81,Default,E,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:11.27,Default,E,0,0,0,,That's what I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:16.15,Default,E,0,0,0,,And I will kill every\Nlast Titan in existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.65,0:23:58.20,Default,E,0,0,0,,A failure as a soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.98,0:24:00.95,Default,E,0,0,0,,Swearing revenge against the Titans,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.95,0:24:03.47,Default,E,0,0,0,,Eren becomes a trainee.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:07.01,Default,E,0,0,0,,But when he fails at basic training,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,he must confront a harsh reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:10.89,Default,E,0,0,0,,A Dim Light in the Darkness of Despair\NHumanity Rises Again (1)
